All services are now running successfully! Here's a summary of the fixes:

## Issues Found and Fixed

### 1. Port Conflicts in `docker-compose.yml`
The metrics ports (9090-9099) conflicted with:
- **Port 9090**: Prometheus service
- **Port 9093**: Alertmanager service

### 2. Solution: Remapped Metrics Ports
Changed all service metrics ports from 9090-9099 range to 9101-9111:

| Service | Old Port | New Port |
|---------|----------|----------|
| auth-service | 9091 | 9101 |
| registry-service | 9092 | 9102 |
| job-service | 9093 | 9103 |
| storage-service | 9094 | 9104 |
| notification-service | 9095 | 9105 |
| api-gateway | 9090 | 9106 |
| analytics-service | 9096 | 9107 |
| organization-service | 9097 | 9108 |
| compliance-service | 9098 | 9109 |
| policy-service | 9099 | 9110 |
| m365-integration-service | 9100 | 9111 |

